{"tid":1576300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連環降級】穆迪降港鐵評級展望至「負面」","createTime":"2019-09-17T07:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T09:09:12.000Z","uid":236171,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"957b2b7a0c6f8422dbe91c9c3e8d04810a019563","tid":1576300,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"有請小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568704244954&amp;issue=20190917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568704244954%26issue%3D20190917&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=9782fc08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568704244954%26issue%3D20190917&h=fe24c716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568704244954&amp;issue=20190917</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構穆迪宣布，將港鐵（0066）、港鐵旗下MTR Corporation（C.I.）及九廣鐵路的評級展望，由「穩定」轉為「負面」，這是緊接將香港的Aa2評級由「穩定」轉為「負面」之後，最新的評級行動。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪指出，確定港鐵、MTR Corporation (C.I.)及九鐵的Aa2評級。該行解釋，是次將港鐵及在鐵等評級展望作出改變，原因是隨著香港的評級展望改變，會對政府相關發行人的信貸質素構成負面影響。根據該行對政府相關發行人的聯合違約分析方法，政府的評級及信貸質素對政府相關發行人的支持，是衡量政府相關發行人的一個主要因素。其指，港鐵及九鐵在得到港府的支持下，因此會因應香港的評級及展望非常敏感，並評估過，港鐵及九鐵對政府的依賴程度分別處於高及非常高水平，兩家公司的信貸質素亦與政府有緊密的營運及財務連繫。在評級展望轉為「負面」下，要將港鐵及九鐵的評級提高不大可能。"},{"pid":"d503d7ef4fae23ea7d8281ae719c6de356b124d1","tid":1576300,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"5a5fad704ec90daf9e51d8118469ee132d61293e","tid":1576300,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc3113702b33f956cd5556f39d04236e43ab9ee","tid":1576300,"uid":261505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"不同意只降至負面"},{"pid":"f5651bd1b16da6b83b9a84b03852383384f19fe8","tid":1576300,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78eb73bb8c124baf42b7d3bca78f532873f0241c","tid":1576300,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"所有政府做股東嘅都要跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc0c871e376cd360215796dbb49be2dee82b649","tid":1576300,"uid":274722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"政府淨係識不同意，幾十萬一個月諗下解決方法啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c9c66d00968c98e9d5f714629d9c76b34b2f98","tid":1576300,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e34da8ce0a2280cc16a4baebe20d12b0bce1f1","tid":1576300,"u